As beauty junkies continue to clean up their acts, swapping out virtually every product in their arsenals with plant-based, sustainable alternatives, hair care brands are also getting the memo. From Curlsmith’s silicone-free bonding oil and LolaVie’s chia seed-infused detangler to Rahua’s re-imagined, aloe vera-spiked gel, there’s a farmers market of nouveau natural options for keeping your locks on lock.